TITLE

*Set the defaults for precision simulations
DEFAULTS                                                              PRECISIO
*Define the beam characteristics
BEAM
*Define the beam position
BEAMPOS
GEOBEGIN                                                              COMBNAME
    0    0          
BOX OUTER      -38.0 -25.0 -50.0 57.0 0 0 0 50.0 0 0 0 100.0
BOX BLCKHOLE   -125.0 -125.0 -125.0 250.0 0 0 0 250.0 0 0 0 250.0
RPP Y_UP       -25.0 5.0 13.0 23.0 -49.0 49.0
RPP Y_DOWN     -25.0 5.0 -23.0 -13.0 -49.0 49.0
RPP Y_SIDE     -30.0 -17.5 -23.0 23.0 -49.0 49.0
RPP P_DOWN     -5.0 5.0 -15.0 -5.0 -49 49
RPP P_UP       -5.0 5.0 5.0 15.0 -49.0 49.0
RCC BP_OUTER   0 0 -50 0 0 100 4.9
RCC BP_VACUU   0 0 -50 0 0 100 4.4
END
BLCKHOLE     5 +BLCKHOLE -OUTER
OUTER        5 +OUTER -Y_UP -Y_DOWN -Y_SIDE -P_DOWN -P_UP -BP_OUTER
YOKE         5 +Y_UP
               | +Y_DOWN
               | +Y_SIDE
               | +P_DOWN
               | +P_UP
BP           5 +BP_OUTER -BP_VACUU
VACUUM       5 +BP_VACUU
END
GEOEND
*..+....1....+....2....+....3....+....4....+....5....+....6....+....7..
*Set the random number seed
RANDOMIZ         1.0
ASSIGNMA    BLCKHOLE  BLCKHOLE
ASSIGNMA         AIR     OUTER
ASSIGNMA        IRON      YOKE
ASSIGNMA    BERYLLIU        BP
ASSIGNMA      VACUUM    VACUUM
*Set the number of primary histories to be simulated in the run
START
STOP
